        h1 The Lunar Landscapes of Lanzarote
        p This is a story about a captivating place, approximately 125 km off the coast of Africa. A place you would choose to see for various reasons: its arid volcanic landscapes, the wild and stunning beaches, the taste of a wine with a bit of an ash flavour, the small white villages washed by the Atlantic Ocean. It's the story of Lanzarote, an amazing island in the Canarie.

